ent below with your thoughts & feedback!','https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pbWgD5zA94Q/default.jpg','2017-05-04 14:47:14',13,0,78,0,5333,1,'[\"board\",\"boardgame\",\"boardgames\",\"capstone games\",\"fun\",\"game\",\"golden elephant award finalist\",\"how to play\",\"learn\",\"live\",\"patreon\",\"playthrough\",\"podcast\",\"reprint\",\"teach\",\"teaching\",\"three kingdoms redux\"]');
