INSERT INTO `youtube_videos` (`id`, `video_id`, `youtube_channel_id`, `youtube_category_id`, `title`, `description`, `thumnail_image_url`, `published_at`, `comment_count`, `dislike_count`, `like_count`, `favorite_count`, `view_count`, `is_related`, `tags`) VALUES (10582666,'9zOmbphAhMc',NULL,NULL,'Playing Ink\'d, The Tattoo Game / Tattoo Challenge - Funny Video | NiliPOD','Blog: www.nilipod.com\nInstagram: @nilipod & @idknia | Snapchat: nilipod\n\n\nPlaying Ink\'d / Getting Inked - The Tattoo Guessing Game / YouTubers Play Tattoo Challenge - Funny Video\nWhen I get together with my YouTuber friend JJ, I know we\'re going to have fun filming vlogs and funny videos.  I\'ve wanted us to play The Ink\'d Tattoo Guessing Game for so long now, ever since I saw it on Oli White\'s YouTube channel.  So far, Oli White has played The Tattoo Game with Joe Sugg, Jack Maynard and Caspar Lee, and they are all very funny videos.\n\nIf you want to play this game at home, then don\'t worry - the tattoos are not \'very\' permanent and you can wash them off after the game.  It\'s a bit like playing Pictionary, but on your body instead!  In fairness, JJ did get a bit carried away with his drawings and some lasted on my skin for almost a week!  Some of the things we had to draw included a Broken Heart, Bow Tie, Viagra (I found this so funny - hilarious!), Venus Fly Trap, Zombie, Wrecking Ball, Brain Fart, Rabbits Doing What Rabbits Do Best, Pregnant and a Poison Bottle.\n\nAfter you\'ve picked a game card for the tattoo itself, you then choose another card for the body part.  These body parts include the cheek, forehead, inner arm, knee, shin, shoulder, stomach, thigh and upper arm, amongst other body parts.\n\nInked / Ink\'d - The Tattoo Guessing Game is definitely a great family game and the perfect funny party game / drinking game, although it\'s probably not ideal for young children / kids, unless they are well supervised.  If you want to buy it yourself, then you can get it from Amazon (Ink\'d the Tattoo Family Guessing Drawing Game by Firefox Games), from eBay, and from decent toy shops, such as Smthys and Toys R Us.\n\nThere are lots of funny tattoo videos and vlogs of YouTube, filmed by popular YouTubers, although not so many with this particular game Ink\'d.  My favourite tattoo videos are by Youtubers such as Joe Sugg and Caspar Lee, PewDiePie, MoreTDM, Pop Trigger, jacksepticeye (Funny 10 Second Tattoo), Romeo Lacoste, CaseyNeistat (crazy Mystery Tattoo), BullsEye, daresundays (Tattoo Torture Challenge), JC Caylen, Pop Trigger and Steve-O TV.  And of course, the Oli White video with his brother James, where they are reviewing a spray tattoo kit, is adorable - as these brothers always are.  It\'s called \'Brothers Give Each Other Tattoos\'.  I also really enjoyed the Tattoo Roulette video with One Direction, on The Late Late Show with James Corden. \n\nThanks so much for watching my Ink\'d tattoo guessing game video and for checking out my YouTube channel.  I love vlogging too, and so there are lots of vlogs on my YouTube channel, as well as other funny videos, games, challenges, reviews and makeup tutorials.  A nice random selection of videos!\n\n\nABOUT ME: \nName: Nia\nCamera: Canon 70D (Canon PowerShot G7X for vlogs)\nAge: 14\nFrom: England, UK\nHobbies:  YouTube videos (filming and editing) and photography\nEditor: Final Cut Pro X\nFavourite YouTubers, Vloggers and Funny Videos:  Anything by Dan and Phil (danisnotonfire and amazingphil), ThatcherJoe (Joe Sugg), Caspar Lee, Oli White, Alfie Deyes (PointlessBlog), PewDiePie, Jim Chapman, Tyler Oakley, Joey Graceffa, Prank vs Prank (BFvsGF), and stuff like that!\nFavourite Music Videos: Ed Sheeran, Taylor Swift, Justin Bieber, Adele, Fall Out Boy, Panic at the Disco\n\n\nRELATED GAME AND CHALLENGE VIDEOS:\nGuy Guesses the Price of Girly Things Game, and Tries Them Out! - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-8f_pt4Mf0Y\nExtreme Boom Boom Balloon Explosions, Don\'t Pop It Challenge, Funny Video - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5XRB0lnnKnc\nPlaying Garden Jenga Game, Giant Wooden Tumbling Tower for Outdoors - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ngOrOQeYzag\n\n\nMY LINKS:\nWebsite: http://www.nilipod.com\nYouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/nilipod\nBlog : http://www.nilipod.com/blog.html\nFaceBook : https://www.facebook.com/Nilipod-1522861534695710\nTwitter : https://mobile.twitter.com/nilipod\nInstagram : https://www.instagram.com/nilipod\nInstagram (Personal) : https://www.instagram.com/idknia\nTumblr : http://nilipod.tumblr.com\nSnapchat - nilipod\n\n\nMY FRIEND\'S INSTAGRAM ACCOUNT:\nJJ - @jjjoshuajj\n\n\nP.S. All music isn\'t mine and I do not claim it as my own!\nCREDIT TO: Little Mix - Shout out To My Ex (Neon City Remix) [Progressive House],  Kevin MacLeod and Sophonic Media','https://i.ytimg.com/vi/9zOmbphAhMc/default.jpg','2016-11-13 18:14:52',94,4,140,0,3317,1,'[\"bf\",\"board game\",\"boardgame\",\"boardgames\",\"boy\",\"boyfriend\",\"camping\",\"card game\",\"cards\",\"challenge\",\"children\",\"comedy\",\"drawing game\",\"friend\",\"friends\",\"fun\",\"funny\",\"funny video\",\"game\",\"getting tattoo\",\"gf\",\"girl\",\"girlfriend\",\"guesses\",\"guessing\",\"guessing game\",\"hilarious\",\"ink\'d\",\"inked\",\"inking\",\"kids\",\"party game\",\"pictionary\",\"play\",\"playing\",\"playing boardgame\",\"playing card game\",\"playing game\",\"silly\",\"tattoo\",\"tattoo game\",\"tattoo guessing game\",\"tattoos\",\"teen\",\"teenager\",\"teenagers\",\"teens\",\"tent\",\"video\",\"vlogger\",\"vloggers\",\"youtube\",\"youtuber\",\"youtubers\"]');
